Spec: CLI Error
Purpose:
  Mark expected errors that should be rendered as CLI messages instead of stack traces.

Structure:
  ./cli-error.ts: CLI error implementation.

Owns:
  ./cli-error.ts

Must:
  Expose a @CliError base class.
  Expose @isCliError as a type guard for @CliError values.

Exposes:
  @CliError
  @isCliError
